  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Leone Clan, level 12+ <br />Through many trails and tribulations you have learned more tricks to expand your skills. You gain the following benefits as well as additional effects to the <strong>Relentless Hunter</strong> clan feature;</p><ul><li><p>You gain an additional amount of Fury die equal to your taijutsu modifier (max of +5)</p><ul><li><p><em><strong>Feral Frenzy:</strong></em> When you would end your turn while transformed you may spend 4 Fury die, if you do you may take an additional turn. After the end of the additional turn you gain three ranks of Slowed until the end of your next turn. You may use this once per long rest.</p></li><li><em><strong>Quicken Recovery:</strong></em> At the start of your turn if you would have a hostile condtion on you, you may spend 3 Fury die removing all ranks of one condition of your choice.</li></ul></li></ul>",
